  "voice": [
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_001",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "……这是我的失误。",
      "text_original": "……私のミスでした。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_001.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_002",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "我的选择，和因它而发生的这一切。",
      "text_original": "私の選択、そしてそれによって招かれたこの全ての状況。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_002.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_003",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "直到最后，迎来了这样的结局，我才明白您是对的……",
      "text_original": "結局、この結果にたどり着いて初めて、あなたの方が正しかったことを悟るだなんて……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_003.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_004",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "……我知道，事到如今再来说这些，挺厚脸皮的。但还是拜托您了。",
      "text_original": "……今更図々しいですが、お願いします。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_004.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_005",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "老师。",
      "text_original": "先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_005.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_006",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "我想，您一定会忘记我说的这些话，不过……没关系。",
      "text_original": "きっと私の話は忘れてしまうでしょうが、それでも構いません。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_006.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_007",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "因为您就算什么都不记得了，在相同的情况下，应该还是会做那样的选择吧……",
      "text_original": "何も思い出せなくても、おそらくあなたは同じ状況で、同じ選択をされるでしょうから……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_007.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_008",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "所以……重要的不是经历，是选择。",
      "text_original": "ですから……大事なのは経験ではなく、選択。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_008.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_009",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "很多很多，只有您才能做出的选择。",
      "text_original": "あなたにしかできない選択の数々。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_009.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_010",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "我们以前聊过……关于背负责任之人的话题吧。",
      "text_original": "責任を負う者について、話したことがありましたね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_010.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_011",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "我当时不懂……但是现在，我能理解了。",
      "text_original": "あの時の私には分かりませんでしたが……。今なら理解できます。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_011.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_012",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "身为大人的责任与义务。以及在其延长线上的，您所做出的选择。",
      "text_original": "大人としての、責任と義務。そして、その延長線上にあった、あなたの選択。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_012.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_013",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "甚至还有，您做出选择时的那份心情。",
      "text_original": "それが意味する心延えも。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_013.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_014",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_014.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_015",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "所以，老师。",
      "text_original": "ですから、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_015.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_016",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "您是我唯一可以信任的大人，",
      "text_original": "私が信じられる大人である、あなたになら、",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_016.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_017",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "我相信您一定能找到，通往与这扭曲的终点所截然不同的……",
      "text_original": "この捻じれて歪んだ先の終着点とは、また別の結果を……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_017.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_018",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "另一种结局的正确选项。",
      "text_original": "そこへ繋がる選択肢は……きっと見つかるはずです。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_018.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "Main_11000_019",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "所以，老师，请您一定要……",
      "text_original": "だから先生、どうか……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/Main_11000_019.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "main_103000_001",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "把这份缘分——",
      "text_original": "この、絆を――",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/main_103000_001.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "main_103000_002",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "和我们在一起的回忆……所有那些共同度过的时光……",
      "text_original": "私たちとの思い出……過ごしてきたそのすべての日々を……どうか……。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/main_103000_002.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "main_104000_011",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "珍藏起来。",
      "text_original": "覚えていてください。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/main_104000_011.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "main_104000_012",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "——因为珍贵的东西绝不会消失。",
      "text_original": "――大切なものは、決して消える事はありません。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/main_104000_012.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "main_104000_013",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "没关系的。",
      "text_original": "大丈夫です。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/main_104000_013.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "main_104000_014",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "所以回去吧，老师。",
      "text_original": "ですから――帰りましょう、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/main_104000_014.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "main_104000_015",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "回到我们的所有奇迹停留的地方。",
      "text_original": "私たちの、すべての「奇跡」が、在る場所へ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%20%E8%81%94%E9%82%A6%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E4%BC%9A%E9%95%BF/original/jp/main_104000_015.ogg"
    }
  ],
